<h2>Whats all this?</h2>
Citizen Data is part polemic, part campaign, part how-to.  I beleive that the vast majority of society's decisions can be informed and 
better decided with minimal government involvement.  I know it sounds all libertarian and American, but the technology is already here to collect and share data about all aspects of everyday life.


Data drives activism




